@startuml
start
:The user opens the file browser;
:The user searches for a file or folder;
:The user opens the context menu for the selected item;
:The user selects "Open";
if (Is the backend local?) then (Yes)
:The system asks the operating system to open the path;
else (No)
:The GUI downloads the file and opens the local copy;
endif
stop
@enduml
